book:
PHP Logger Classes
Logger



 &reftitle.intro;


   This extension is a logging framework that wraps the log4cxx lib. Logging is a
   very important tool for tracing an application behaviour and is the only choice 
   when debuggers are not applicable. The core component of the extension is the log4cxx library
   (a log4j implementation in C++).



   Documenting the log4cxx concepts and organization is outside the scope of this documentation. It is
   highly recommended that you read the Short introduction to Apache log4cxx in
   order to understand this extension.




